            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A funnel treats customers as an output — pour prospects in, deals fall out the bottom, done. A flywheel treats customers as an input to the next cycle: their advocacy, retention, and referrals feed acquisition of the next customer.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
